Lilo &amp; Stitch;;77;;86;;PG;;A tale of a young girl's close encounter with the galaxy's most wanted extraterrestrial. Lilo is a lonely Hawaiian girl who adopts a small ugly "dog," whom she names Stitch. Stitch would be the perfect pet if he weren't in reality a genetic experiment who has escaped from an alien planet and crash-landed on Earth. Through her love, faith and unwavering belief in ohana, the Hawaiian concept of family, Lilo helps unlock Stitch's heart and gives him the ability to care for someone else.;;Animation,Kids & family,Comedy;;Dean DeBlois,Christopher Sanders;;2002;;Daveigh Chase,Christopher Sanders,Tia Carrere,David Ogden Stiers,Kevin McDonald,Ving Rhames,Zoe Caldwell,Jason Scott Lee,Kevin Michael Richardson,Susan Hegarty,Amy Hill;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lilo_and_stitch